      <title>特朗普法官因审判计划“有缺陷”而受到检察官的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-judge-assailed-by-prosecutor-over-flawed-trial-planning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因不当处理机密文件而起诉前总统唐纳德·特朗普的司法部特别检察官向负责此案的法官表达了不满，称她对关键法律问题的理解似乎“存在根本缺陷”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-judge-assailed-by-prosecutor-over-flawed-trial-planning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 04:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示莫迪联盟将在印度主要邦赢得最多选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/modi-alliance-to-win-most-votes-in-key-india-state-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据全国选举前两周的一项民意调查，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的联盟预计将在该国人口最多的邦获得多数选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/modi-alliance-to-win-most-votes-in-key-india-state-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 01:53:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>模型显示，特朗普的关税计划将提高美国人的物价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-60-tariff-on-china-10-elsewhere-to-raise-us-inflation-model</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博经济研究在一份报告中表示，唐纳德·特朗普誓言要实施的关税计划可能会导致通胀超过美联储的目标，并迫使央行加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-60-tariff-on-china-10-elsewhere-to-raise-us-inflation-model</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 01:30:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本知事因反对高速新干线而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/japan-governor-opposing-high-speed-bullet-train-to-resign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地报道，日本某市政府的知事、长期批评建造世界上最快火车计划的人因公众言论嘲笑农民而受到批评，目前正在辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/japan-governor-opposing-high-speed-bullet-train-to-resign</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>援助人员死亡后拜登升级对以色列的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/biden-outraged-by-aid-worker-deaths-calls-for-accountability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，在七名援助人员死亡后，以色列在保护平民方面做得不够，这是他对该国在加沙发起针对哈马斯军事行动几个月来的行为的最严厉批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/biden-outraged-by-aid-worker-deaths-calls-for-accountability</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:21:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩领导测试可击中美国基地的新型导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/kim-jong-un-leads-test-of-new-missile-that-can-hit-us-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝鲜官方媒体报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩监督了新型弹道导弹的测试，该导弹旨在部署可运载核弹头的高超音速滑翔飞行器，并称这次测试是“划时代的成功”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/kim-jong-un-leads-test-of-new-missile-that-can-hit-us-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:19:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理在电话中向内塔尼亚胡表达愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/australian-pm-expresses-anger-to-netanyahu-at-aid-worker-s-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞表示，他在与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的电话中对一名澳大利亚援助人员的死亡表达了“愤怒和担忧”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/australian-pm-expresses-anger-to-netanyahu-at-aid-worker-s-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 23:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于医疗改革停滞，石油公司对哥伦比亚保险公司采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/colombia-watchdog-to-intervene-sanitas-health-insurer-blu-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）的政府已开始控制哥伦比亚最大的私人保险公司之一，因为他改革医疗系统的尝试在国会陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/colombia-watchdog-to-intervene-sanitas-health-insurer-blu-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 23:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
